{"tid":1671611,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"突發 有人想自廢武功 全世界入嚟幫拖啊！","createTime":"2019-10-23T14:56:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T17:08:21.000Z","uid":167548,"like":15,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"42782df74d25b85cbcb7a065b61a36696e35e77a","tid":1671611,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T14:56:52.000Z","msg":"[ 撤離焦土 ] 連  登  不  信  任  動  議<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/epzoJS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/epzoJS</a><br />\n<blockquote><br />\n我諗呢個係我最後一個公投<br />\n大家知道港共中共一路以連登作為指標、分化同滲透對象<br />\n因此好大部份既手足已唔再將連登當成可信任既資訊來源，但係有唔少人仍然真心膠以為連登消息代表一切<br />\n<br />\n所以趁連登仲有人，我想做一個表態公投，想知各位連登仔是否認為從今以後<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">連登上所有言論已經喪失參考性</span></span></strong>而且不可相信<br />\n<br />\n正評：是<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(535)<br />\n負評：否<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(305)<br />\n2019-10-23 23:55<br />\n</blockquote><span style=\"color: green;\"><strong><br />\n<br />\n個位樓豬可唔可以唔好做蠢事啊, 明明出過好多正能量POST, 就因為連登有打手, 今日o既挫敗就自爆, 玩自廢武功<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp;過埋聽晚就咩事都沒架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span>"},{"pid":"8f60bbf2b883af0cb418ef3ae7237698f0c26048","tid":1671611,"uid":167548,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T14:57:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">#76愛情波函數</span><br />\n呢個係paradox，因為五毛都可以投<br />\n如果五毛的確係多過香港人，佢地投是，咁答案姐係否，佢地投否，答案姐係是，反之亦然。<br />\n姐係呢個post係冇撚用既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eb02f526c9e1087102d1afff9a2c272b9f9753c","tid":1671611,"uid":45206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T14:57:52.000Z","msg":"可能佢想逼連仔"},{"pid":"f587af17